comments: Oladipo (MIA) is moving alongside Dort's (OKC) path and marginal body contact occurs as they come together during the drive. The foot to foot contact that occurs is incidental.
Adebayo (MIA) fails to fully clear the lane and is in the paint for longer than three seconds without imminently actively guarding an opponent.
Lowry (MIA) initiates contact with Gilgeous-Alexander's (OKC) arm that affects his ability to make the pass.
Dort (OKC) jumps from point A to point B and makes contact with Oladipo (MIA), which affects his play at the basket.
Oladipo (MIA) swipes up and lightly brushes Gilgeous-Alexander's (OKC) arm and marginal contact occurs.
Lowry (MIA) makes clean contact with the ball and dislodges it away from Gilgeous-Alexander (OKC) at the end of the drive.

call_type: Turnover: Lost Ball Out of Bounds
comments: Replay review of the out of bounds called on Lowry (MIA) pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed successful. Gilgeous-Alexander (OKC) touches the ball last before going out of bounds.
Adebayo (MIA) maintains his arms within the frame of his body and does not deliver illegal contact to Gilgeous-Alexander (OKC) during the pick.
Gilgeous-Alexander (OKC) and Adebayo (MIA) come together in pursuit of the loose ball and marginal contact occurs during the rebound.
Gilgeous-Alexander (OKC) gathers the ball on his right foot and hops consecutively on it.
Adebayo (MIA) initiates contact with Gilgeous-Alexander's (OKC) arm that affects his SQBR.
Martin (MIA) establishes himself in a slightly wide stance, but he firms up and absorbs the marginal contact with Dort (OKC) to his upper body.
Martin (MIA) touches the ball last before going out of bounds.
Martin (MIA) legally contests Gilgeous-Alexander's (OKC) jump shot attempt. Any "high-five" contact after the release is considered incidental.
Dedmon (MIA) extends a hand into Giddey's (OKC) back, which affects his shot attempt near the rim.
